254
00:19:00,420 --> 00:19:01,660
who kidnapped Miss Luo.

255
00:19:04,660 --> 00:19:05,860
A powerful figure of Beichu.

256
00:19:06,220 --> 00:19:07,060
He's from Nanyue.

257
00:19:07,420 --> 00:19:08,980
