268
00:19:28,860 --> 00:19:30,460
Zhao Yuan, watch over the military camp.

269
00:19:30,460 --> 00:19:31,300
Yes, sir.

270
00:19:31,580 --> 00:19:32,600
I'm going to save Lingyu.

271
00:19:33,580 --> 00:19:34,420
